<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Before 30 September each year, the Commission shall adopt an annual plan for the distribution of the products from intervention stocks, broken down by Member State concerned. </inglise>
