<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Implementation of the plan shall run from 1 October to 30 September of the following year. It shall cover the withdrawal of products from intervention stocks from 1 October to 31 August. </inglise>
