<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> For EAGGF Guarantee Section accounting purposes, and notwithstanding the provisions of Article 8 of Council Regulation (EEC) No 1883/78 (8), the accounting value of the products made available from intervention under this Regulation shall be the intervention price applicable on 1 October of each year. </inglise>
